summary: Believes in the potential of the private sector in developing countries to empower people to move up on the social-economic ladder. Strong focus on corporate social responsibility. On the ground experience in private sector development and project management in Africa. Clear understanding of international business and finance. Strong analytical skills, result driven and capable of interacting effectively in a multi-cultural work environment.
